rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>5 Reasons Why Blume Can Start Clearing Years of Hormonal Acne—In Just 3 Days</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="cc80da3a-a164-4677-80bb-5b7efff8b1ce" class="r-okp7tk alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Hormonal acne isn’t just a phase—it’s painful, unpredictable, and feels like it will never go away.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Maybe it shows up every month like clockwork. Maybe it’s taken over your jawline, cheeks, or forehead. Maybe your skin is extra sensitive—and every product you’ve tried either does nothing or leaves it dry, red, and breaking out even more.</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">You’re not alone.</span></p><p><br><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Blume’s Clear Skin Kit was made for skin just like yours</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">: sensitive, breakout-prone, and exhausted from years of trial and error. It’s powered by clean, proven ingredients that treat hormonal acne at the source—</span><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">without the harsh side effects</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">.</span></p><br><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Whether you're a girl or a boy, 11, 18, in your 30s or 50+, this routine was designed to work across all life stages and skin types. And for many customers? </span><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">It starts making a visible difference in just 3 days.</span></strong></p><p><br></p></span></div>{%- comment -%}replo-liquid-chunk-begin{%- endcomment -%}<a data-rid="24f336aa-eb60-46e2-9715-1fd56c04f9b7" tabindex="0" role="link" class="text r-12g1vmg alchemy-rte" href="https://www.blume.com/products/clear-skin-kit-3?utm_term=utm_term=har-v2a-cta2"><div data-rid="5048786d-fd51-497c-8b23-18bd1265a8e5" class="r-1qfrb4e alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>STOP ACNE NOW -  SAVE 30%</p></span></div></a>{%- comment -%}replo-liquid-chunk-end{%- endcomment -%}</div></div><div data-rid="3566a2f9-a6b3-45a2-9409-31e70a74ebfe" class="r-rry0yu"><div data-rid="42fa1727-8ed8-4b38-b424-7282864d68ad" class="r-1uhus6g"><div data-rid="a508205a-6079-49c8-872e-e344480cf024" class="r-twofdx"><div data-rid="5aa8a848-e971-4d31-9812-44a3479dfe03" class="r-dbogpq alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Here’s why Blume works when nothing else has:</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="e3e62ff1-bc86-49e4-ac66-433c4e9ba519" class="r-1vhkyv3"><div data-rid="36aaa0a0-9310-43be-a555-9e54f13e5c2e" class="r-y18rmy alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>1. This Oil Treats Hormonal Acne at the Root—And It’s Clinically Proven</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="0ad07337-ba1e-4eee-81c3-adf6f389b09f" class="r-4ya4tw alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Most acne products sit on the surface of your skin, drying out pimples without addressing what’s </span><em><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">causing</span></em><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"> them. Blume’s Clear Skin Kit is different.</span></p><br><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">It’s powered by a proprietary blend of non-comedogenic oils, including a high concentration (25%) of black cumin seed oil—one of the only natural ingredients clinically proven to fight hormonal acne below the surface.</span></p><br><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Because it’s an oil, it doesn’t just sit on top—it absorbs deep into the skin, where hormonal breakouts begin, and helps flatten acne before it ever reaches the surface.</span></p></span></div><div data-rid="c0e5a490-ce9c-4783-9bbd-0a23e2d52ac5" class="r-1kyv6y6 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>🔬 The secret? Thymoquinone, the bioactive compound in black cumin seed oil.</p></span></div><div data-rid="2c61dff5-fd71-4a26-99cd-5a8af549fb56" class="r-1mczp30"><div data-rid="51191503-f5ff-4911-85fe-f915ae43e695" class="r-1p8oj2n"><div data-rid="c67f3608-645b-4a47-a1af-bf76acda0714" class="r-1scskos"><s