0ebd0466a34" class="r-b66y8i"><span style="display:contents"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="feather feather-arrow-right" style="fill: none;stroke: currentColor;width: var(--rsw, 100%);height: 100%" role="presentation"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline></svg></span></div><div data-rid="dec68dc9-c83e-405e-b432-65e3d86b1f0b" class="r-s1669z alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">It’s also been shown to </span><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">inhibit the growth of Cutibacterium acnes</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">, the bacteria deeply involved in acne development.</span></p></span></div></div></div><div data-rid="371c2516-05f3-4b16-b612-229bb3e51e9f" class="r-m0cq1y alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>🌿 Here’s how it works:</p></span></div><div data-rid="167bbce3-2dd1-4ce1-bb16-529115f8f423" class="r-151jtaj alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><ul><li><p><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Antibacterial:</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"> Kills breakout-causing bacteria deep in your pores—without harsh chemicals or antibiotics.</span></p></li><li><p><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Anti-inflammatory:</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"> Calms the hormone-triggered redness, swelling, and pain you feel under the skin.</span></p></li><li><p><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Sebum-regulating:</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"> Balances oil production to prevent both clogged pores </span><em><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">and</span></em><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"> dry, flaky skin.</span></p></li></ul></span></div><div data-rid="5f3409f3-e868-4e66-bca5-c25041f73eef" class="r-1v8tpqb alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">And unlike traditional acne treatments that can damage your barrier or cause rebound breakouts, black cumin seed oil is </span><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">non-comedogenic, hydrating, and safe for daily use</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">—even on sensitive skin.</span></p></span></div><div data-rid="75170175-8af4-40b4-bb61-0f78dcd4bbd0" class="r-trx4b6 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><strong>You’re not just treating what’s visible. You’re preventing what’s coming next.</strong></p></span></div><picture data-rid="86de15d4-116a-4ff1-8679-6685d1a2c260" class="r-1ez2h32"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/ec24001e-3a95-4635-9569-fd967df2ca65?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/ec24001e-3a95-4635-9569-fd967df2ca65?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/ec24001e-3a95-4635-9569-fd967df2ca65?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/ec24001e-3a95-4635-9569-fd967df2ca65" class="r-1fvhrlj" loading="eager"/></picture>{%- comment -%}replo-liquid-chunk-begin{%- endcomment -%}<a data-rid="e4ea8b69-73bf-4090-8869-bdff36508a0c" tabindex="0" role="link" class="text r-tbo7u5 alchemy-rte" href="https://www.blume.com/products/clear-skin-kit-3?utm_term=utm_term=har-v2a-cta3"><div data-rid="4f2d5090-1d9f-44d9-806e-0384b6df9105" class="r-1huc1yo alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>STOP ACNE NOW -  SAVE 30%</p></span></div></a>{%- comment -%}replo-liquid-chunk-end{%- endcomment -%}</div></div><div data-rid="81f7023f-99d4-4c0e-b10d-c6c2fbe1de93" class="r-s0lvxi"><div data-rid="7cc52601-d4e1-4736-a6ae-70d782448861" class="r-1iiclw"><div data-rid="6ed31448-d6ba-41bf-9cc8-094adf906deb" class="r-9l85r9"><div data-rid="128091d7-dc62-4c2d-ab00-50f6f73247f8" class="r-axewgq alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>2. A Clinically Backed Routine That Rebuilds Your Skin While It Clears It</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="cfee3a86-2684-48a2-9407-4dfb2b58c2ec" class="r-9pgkv1 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Most acne products are too aggressive. They kill bacteria, but they also strip your skin—damaging your moisture barrier and leaving you with more breakouts, irritation, and redness than when you started.</p><p><br></p><p><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Blume’s Clear Skin Kit does the opposite.</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"> It’s a 3-step routine made to </span><em><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">treat breakouts</span></em><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"> while actively repairing and strengthening your skin barrier—so you’re not just clearing your skin, you’re restoring it.</span></p><br></span></div><div data-rid="1a8a2c2e-fb3e-45d0-945c-d2cc9ee09ec7" class="r-3t72lw"><div class="r-yc13or" data-rid="1"><div data-rid="b7d1c6f4-620f-4f53-8aad-674277541018" class="r-o190pe"><div data-rid="e39a9834-7c60-45ed-bda0-748411c99f86" class="r-1952lzx alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Each ingredient was carefully chosen to <strong>heal, hydrate, and protect acne-prone skin</strong>:</p></span></div><div data-rid="9173e47d-aec6-47f2-8589-9842b3864a17" class="r-qchcke" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="4b563dd2-38e8-4505-8e87-8f9c9b6b6d94" class="r-ah95q0" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="b41aeb7d-74fe-4c48-bbac-32f46bc410ac" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rb9p32:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1x9fief"><div data-rid="79a7b0f5-a79a-481f-8a77-1ca198b8693e" class="r-q63qck alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><strong>Ceramides</strong></p></span></div><div data-rid="2e6c42ff-4b27-40ce-a2f2