0%"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">A plant-derived humectant clinically shown to:</span></p><ul><li><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Increase skin hydration by up to 35% in just 7 days</span></p></li><li><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Maintain moisture balance to prevent overproduction of oil</span></p></li><li><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Soften dry, reactive skin while visibly improving texture and tone</span></p></li></ul></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="7b81ff02-61f6-4862-b715-3157f4ff29b0" class="r-1q30s7o alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Glycerin draws moisture into your skin and keeps it there—strengthening your barrier and making your skin less reactive to stress, hormones, and inflammation. And because it’s non-comedogenic, it’s safe for daily use—even on sensitive, acne-prone skin.</span></p></span></div><div data-rid="ec02f91d-6447-41ad-b3cc-28dc0f8ae545" class="r-1btwn9p alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>The result?</p></span></div><div data-rid="87af2b8f-9147-4166-97d9-803cbd1b565f" class="r-w3dunk alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">A routine that works </span><em><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">with</span></em><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"> your skin, not against it.</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"><br></span><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">✨ Repaired barrier<br>✨ Deep hydration<br>✨ Fewer flare-ups over time</span></strong></p><p><br><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Instead of causing new problems, this kit helps your skin recover—and stay clear for good.</span></p></span></div><div data-rid="0865a1d3-ce2e-4359-b91e-ac702cce0d55" class="r-cutjkc"><div data-rid="4dcf73b5-310c-4d0d-a79a-a77e3f438328" class="r-mc8qvp alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>After 1 Month</p></span></div><div data-rid="30e9b7f9-d944-41b2-80ce-19304de0adf3" class="r-19emrbn"><div data-rid="204e