pan style="width:100%"><p>From a consumer perception study of 23 participants between the ages of 16 and 63, over 1 month</p></span></div></div></div><div data-rid="3be9823b-c445-49bc-bcbd-d8e35ba14e7f" class="r-xaioq1"><div data-rid="0badcd25-7adc-4e0a-a900-dd191d23dd96" class="r-9c6vvr"><div data-rid="9a28f9e5-7276-42f6-a680-90d7302104af" class="r-7qtp90"><div data-rid="9095c294-f9a2-409b-91ac-13727ac2db49" class="r-w6ep4w alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>3. Hydration That Won’t Clog Pores (Yes, It’s Possible)</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="e800dff2-a976-4548-9f4b-cf7535cb8fb0" class="r-u8d3fo alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">If you’ve ever been told that moisturizers or oils will make your acne worse, you’re not alone—and you’ve also been misled. The truth is, dehydrated skin is more likely to break out. When your skin lacks moisture, it overcompensates by producing excess oil—clogging pores and triggering more hormonal flare-ups.</span></p><br><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">The Clear Skin Kit is designed to break that cycle.</span></p><br><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Every step in the routine delivers deep, lasting hydration while staying completely non-comedogenic—meaning it won't clog your pores or trigger new breakouts. Instead of heavy creams or harsh treatments, you get lightweight, breathable hydration that keeps your skin balanced, calm, and clear.</span></p><br><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">You don’t have to choose between being breakout-free and well-hydrated. Blume makes sure you get both—without the fear.</span></p><p><br></p></span></div><div data-rid="a5b19125-19f3-456a-a11b-ecaf0ef0e861" class="r-zvs4ut"><picture data-rid="54a9bc4e-66aa-4747-874a-8109633226bd" class="r-2kdxf5"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/d3ed28a8-f6a7-48c8-990f-a1ab9bf9d7ad/10ea4be0-9f33-4042-8760-d84edc4e3860?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.re