="r-rstona"><div data-rid="43a0d172-a566-41e5-b74f-f2796a38bfce" class="r-1nho96p"><div data-rid="f6fd6310-ac86-4954-ae5f-eff990d3b14d" class="r-14dw9jn"><div data-rid="512595ff-460c-4a1e-aa9a-2a450b6fad0d" class="r-7uxiln alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>4. Not Just Treatment—Real Prevention That Works</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="d3921d7a-a249-4a66-9a87-10dfb387442d" class="r-jyjrnu alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>You’ve probably cleared a breakout before—only for it to come back a week later, sometimes worse. That’s because most acne products only treat the surface symptoms, not the root cause.</p><br><p>Hormonal acne is different. It starts deep under the skin, often showing up as painful, swollen cysts that are hard to treat and slow to heal. By the time they surface, they’re already too stubborn for most spot treatments. That’s where the Clear Skin Kit comes in.</p><br><p>This 3-step routine is designed to work beneath the surface. The oil-based treatment absorbs into the skin to flatten pimples before they even come up. The gentle cleanser deeply cleans without stripping, leaving your skin soft and balanced. And the oil-free gel cream keeps your skin hydrated and your barrier protected—without clogging pores.</p><br><p>What makes the Clear Skin Kit different? Every ingredient is chosen to not only treat active breakouts but to help prevent future ones from forming. The formulas calm inflammation, reduce redness, and clear congestion—all without harsh chemicals that can irritate or dry out your skin.</p><br><p>With consistent use, your skin becomes clearer, calmer, and more resilient—so you’re no longer stuck in a cycle of breakouts, scarring, and overcorrection.</p><br><p><strong>Clear skin shouldn’t be a short-term win.</strong> With Blume, it’s something you can maintain.<br></p></span></div><picture data-rid="879ba686-d467-4fbd-b230-bc05fb224202" class="r-p1k802"><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/file