role="button" class="r-1028bxe"><div data-rid="3b50b40c-1611-4249-b0cb-91b6a44518f8" class="r-1q8jajs alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Can boys use the Clear Skin Kit?</p></span></div><div data-rid="e9a51310-3f6d-422f-a154-db5b35b1516e" class="r-9pujzi"><span style="display:contents"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="feather feather-plus-circle" style="fill: none;stroke: currentColor;width: var(--rsw, 100%);height: 100%" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="16"></line><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"></line></svg></span></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:Rqr2:" aria-controls="replo-:Rqr2:"><div data-rid="be376783-60d4-47e1-a7f3-329568b87efe" class="r-wltesr"><div data-rid="0d3214a4-717f-4802-900d-f2bf2591dd7e" class="r-1ca9ado alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>100%! Acne doesn’t discriminate—and neither do we. The Clear Skin Kit is gender-neutral and designed for all skin types, including teenage and adult male skin. Many of our customers (and their parents!) love the results for boys dealing with hormonal or stubborn acne.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="acff45c4-6195-4e10-86a9-8ab08f56afed" class="r-iv0wel" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="07f6da67-c987-4dca-83a5-e052fa77df55" aria-controls="replo-:R1ar2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-ytusxs"><div data-rid="74113642-600a-42f3-b072-e051fecdf1d6" class="r-5274by alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Is it safe for teens?</p></span></div><div data-rid="168d178c-8158-4487-9fc7-19e383bb3d91" class="r-1suvug2"><span style="display:contents"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="feather feather-plus-circle" style="fill: none;stroke: currentColor;width: var(--rsw, 100%);height: 100%" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="16"></line><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"></line></svg></span></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R1ar2:" aria-controls="replo-:R1ar2:"><div data-rid="b8ab7956-9666-4fde-8bbd-97d36f502a69" class="r-n14wb7"><div data-rid="d59802f9-7083-4cfc-8e75-bdf5fd2c556e" class="r-1stvzcy alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Yes. The Clear Skin Kit is safe and gentle enough for preteens and teens—especially those just starting to experience breakouts from puberty or hormone changes. No harsh ingredients, no scary side effects—just real results.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="582a4bc8-f407-45f1-9dd5-8c2d2bc38245" class="r-18defcg" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="b6c4bcb8-1be8-4d2f-a0e7-a5d8e04b32af" aria-controls="replo-:R1qr2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-50evpr"><div data-rid="7b47e05d-d576-4bd8-a857-2b3a5fb5bf8d" class="r-1y2o8no alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Can I use it while pregnant or breastfeeding?</p></span></div><div data-rid="45d90faa-297c-4c04-b608-bb697a6da288" class="r-1ehnp5k"><span style="display:contents"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="feather feather-plus-circle" style="fill: none;stroke: currentColor;width: var(--rsw, 100%);height: 100%" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="16"></line><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"></line></svg></span></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R1qr2:" aria-controls="replo-:R1qr2:"><div data-rid="d86516c4-6ec8-4f0c-973d-adf608e44704" class="r-5nq61h"><div data-rid="67dbecba-acee-433e-9aa0-487fb09c1052" class="r-n4927z alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>While all of our ingredients are clean and considered safe, we always recommend checking with your healthcare provider before starting any new skincare routine during pregnancy or while breastfeeding, just to be extra cautious.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="42c958fb-2ae0-44f8-b8a8-e399e73cd39f" class="r-155y9ey" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="61cbf1a4-c792-41af-b5db-678a83e0d89a" aria-controls="replo-:R2ar2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-j5gqm8"><div data-rid="2f44b610-be10-430c-92df-02fff7cfe62a" class="r-16y4t6a alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What’s the right order to use the products in the kit?</p></span></div><div data-rid="08b6aad3-694b-4e31-84fb-bd292d83bc1e" class="r-1q27upq"><span style="display:contents"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="feather feather-plus-circle" style="fill: none;stroke: currentColor;width: var(--rsw, 100%);height: 100%" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="16"></line><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"></line></svg></span></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R2ar2:" aria-controls="replo-:R2ar2:"><div data-rid="7b468643-6dac-4416-b9cc-c319a9d86ba6" class="r-n3x5yr"><div data-rid="af26fae6-7209-4de5-a1df-85f0baa4bdfe" class="r-10th8sg alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Great question! Use them in this order, twice daily (morning and night):</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">1 - Cleanse with Meltdown Cleanser</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">2 - Spot treat with Meltdown Oil</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">3 - Moisturize with Meltdown Gel Cream</span></p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-r